Section.
FY 2027 Base Plans:
Complete Developmental Test and Verification static fire testing, conduct an In Process Review (IPR) to
establish the initial product design and begin qualification and insensitive munitions testing at the rocket motor
level. Complete the Ballistic Test Vehicle -2 design and execute live fire to demonstrate the qualified rocket
motor design in a flight test environment.
