 virtual and physical environment. Using enhancements to the Adaptive Squad Architecture (ASA) digital tools verify
 development of interface controls documents, and connection points to support the rapid integration of the CCIE programs with all other dismounted Soldier equipment.
 Prototype capabilities for evaluation and integration include new measurements and methodologies from S&T programs and future requirements. Funding for this
 program aligns with the Army's priorities in support of Digital Engineering and Transformation and is a Soldier
 Lethality Cross Functional Team priority.

