revision from DDG(X) to BBG(X) IPS requirement for incorporation of hardware. Procure and test prototypical
material to validate the power and propulsion architecture design. Continue refinement of interfaces and
specifications for individual power and propulsion system and validation of Digital Engineering efforts.
